Title: Establishes a task force to examine, evaluate and determine the feasibility of establishing a state-funded version of SNAP
Summary: Establishes a task force to examine, evaluate and determine the feasibility of establishing a state-funded version of SNAP; requires the task force to report its findings and a policy brief to the governor and the legislature.
ActClause: AN ACT in relation to establishing a task force to study the feasibility of a state-funded SNAP; and providing for the repeal of such provisions upon expiration thereof
